author: 21crow73
body: Mid May 2024.... when I first saw KENDU I swore I wouldn't buy into another dog meme coin. I told this to myself over and over for weeks. I was only interested in utility coins. I kept seeing post after post and saw the passion in them. Saw the positive comments and just overall genuine belief in people that this was truly a unique project.  Then, one day, scrolling through posts I felt that belief too. It truly is a unique feeling. And I know even those that have sold and moved on to buying into other project are keeping their eyes on KENDU. Because they Know KENDU will become one of the biggest meme coins we've ever seen.
